  "response": "\"Death Note II: The Last Name\" can be watched dubbed in English on various streaming platforms. Here are some options where you might find it:\n\n1. **Netflix**: Depending on your region, Netflix may offer the English dubbed version of the movie.\n2. **Crunchyroll**: This platform often has a selection of anime movies and series with English dubs.\n3. **Funimation**: Known for its extensive library of dubbed anime, Funimation might have \"Death Note II: The Last Name\" available.\n4. **Amazon Prime Video**: You can check if the movie is available for streaming or purchase with an English dub.\n5. **Hulu**: Hulu sometimes carries anime movies and series with English dubs.\n\nAvailability can vary by region, so you may need to check each service to see if it's offered in your area. If you're having trouble finding it on streaming services, you might also look into purchasing a DVD or Blu-ray version that includes the English dub.",
